AOE skills to clear the field</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440750/extras/ff4dacb63172a46b3b0ac09568cceeff.poster.avif?t=1743088734\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440750/extras/ff4dacb63172a46b3b0ac09568cceeff.webm?t=1743088734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>After continuously killing enemies and entering COMBO state, weapons and equipment will receive additional effect bonuses!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maintaining the COMBO state without interruption is the key</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440750/extras/5bea1914c4d636a826009f8e49c6406b.poster.avif?t=1743088734\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440750/extras/5bea1914c4d636a826009f8e49c6406b.webm?t=1743088734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440750/extras/5bea1914c4d636a826009f8e49c6406b.mp4?t=1743088734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30+ itms available for unlocking!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440750/extras/019e92275663cefdbb570962129bff4b.poster.avif?t=1743088734\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440750/extras/019e92275663cefdb